[SN]TITLE[SN]
Make Your Move Q&A - with Michael Johnson, Paula Radcliffe & Greg Whyte

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Are you just finding your feet with running? Or are you already a runner and want some tips?

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
BBC Get Inspired held a live Facebook Q&A with 13-time Olympic and World Championship gold medallist Michael Johnson and four-time Olympian and marathon world record holder Paula Radcliffe.
Physical activity expert Professor Greg Whyte was also on hand to answer any questions you have to help you with your running.
You can re-live the whole session here.
And if you still want to get involved with the conversation, join us on Twitter and Facebook using #MakeYourMove or @BBCGetInspired.
